---
title: Southern Double Pork Chops with White BBQ Sauce, Buttery Corn and Crispy Potatoes
description: Delicious seared pork chops are a match made in heaven for creamy, buttery corn and a zingy white BBQ sauce. This Southern-style BBQ sauce is mayo-based with a kick of horseradish!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/double-cotelettes-de-porc-a-la-mode-du-sud-3829c60f.jpg
